headline: Walgreens Boots Alliance (WBA) Q3 Earnings and Revenues Beat Estimates
summary: Walgreens (WBA) delivered earnings and revenue surprises of +11.76% and +6.49%, respectively, for the quarter ended May 2025. Do the numbers hold clues to what lies ahead for the stock?
